      • addStation

        public void addStation(String name,
              double latitude,
              double longitude,
              double elevation,
              double delay,
              double fmag,
              double xmag,
              int sysNum)
                throws IllegalArgumentException
        Add station to station list.
        Parameters:
        name - station name
        latitude - station latitude in DD
        longitude - station longitude in DD
        elevation - in meters
        delay - station delay
        fmag - station correction for coda magnitude (FMAG)
        xmag - station correction for local magnitude (XMAG)
        sysNum - system number assigned to station so that the frequency response curve of the seismometer and preamp is specified for the amplitude magnitude calculation. (E.g. use 0 for Wood-Anderson)
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException
